reviews: Nice minimalist look, these bookends looks teallu neat!

I love this organizer, I use in the car between the car seats to keep snacks, water bottles, blankets, plush toys etc... for my girls. It really helped with the clutter in the back seat. I love the many pockets to keep everything in place.

The fabric of the canopy is really nice, kinda like flour sack material, it's heavy enough that it stays in place and hang nicely, however, the color is really more of a bubble gum pink instead of a dusty pink like I wanted. I will keep it anyway. Just be aware, the color is nowhere near a dusty pink or "vintage" pink like pictured.

This bracelet is so pretty, and it looks more expensive than it is! The finish and the writing doesn't fade. The rose gold is really nice. You can also adjust it since it fits a little large, now the fit fit is perfect on my small wrist.

This hat is so cute! The fit is great, love the adjustable band around the head. Very light, large enough to keep the neck and face in the shade. It also washes well and dry pretty fast. I would buy more for sure.
Product is really soft, washes well, easy to install on the bed. Great buy! I definitely recommend it.

These headbands are soft and cute but not at all the same colors as pictured. The white one is a light yellow, the mustard one is orange/peach, the burgundy is more of a purple, the dusty pink is more of a light pink and the dark blue is black. I'm disappointed and I will try to find someone who wants half of these headbands since I wont use them all due to their color.
Very cute, lightweight, perfect for little hands. Would buy more toys from this company for sure! The images are really cute and the colors are great.

I wasn't expecting much from these diapers but I was pleasantly surprised! The colours and patterns are great, they wash well, the fit is good on my baby, the inserts are easy to install. These diapers are a good find! I am really pleased with my purchase. I combine one microfibre insert with one bamboo insert ( bought separately) and my baby stay dry for at least 3 hours. So far, no leaks with these diapers and no stains.

The bag is pretty roomy, plenty of space for my lunch and my breakfast. Got a lot of compliments on it, the fabric seems sturdy and good quality. Easy to wash, I like the dual zipper. Would recommend!
Perfect for my need, holds a lot of diapers, strong fabric, nice pattern.
This mat is so cute! Very practical. We use it when we go see some family, I just put a blanket or two in it and lots of toys, everything stays inside.
My baby loves that rattle, and it's so pretty! Good weight, I imagine she will play with it for a long time.
These bags are really cute, I use them when I go to the pool for wet swimming suits, or to carry dry and wet cloth diapers and even to carry my baby's lunch items (water bottle, puree pouches etc...)
